:51.000Z","fixedOddsUpdateTime":"2026-04-11T22:43:39.000Z","raceComments":"{\"comment\":\"5. CHIPILLY returned from a 5-month break in terrific order, putting her rivals away by 3 lengths over 1100m here. She has a strong track record, and the extra 200m is the ideal next step. She has always promised a lot, and now that she is stronger, she can repeat the dose, especially with 2.5kg less to carry. 1. PLEASE MIZTER is a stablemate of the first pick, and he was sound enough when resuming over 1200m, finishing sixth over 1200m. He generally improves sharply second-up and has 2 top 3 finishes at this stage of a prep, so he is among the each-way hopes. 10. LACIE ACE was not far away when fourth over 1200m here last start and finds a suitable race. With even luck, she can be competitive. Include in all combinations. 2. WEST COAST WARRIOR resumes after 12 weeks and now joins the Joanna Offen yard. He has won fresh up in the past, and a change of scenery can often work wonders. Use the market as the best guide.\",\"runners\":[5,1,10,2],\"exclusive\":true}","ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,6,1,11]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,7,6,9]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,10,1,9]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,10,5,8]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,9,4,5]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[6,11,5,7]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,5,6,10]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"KAL","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"KAL","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"KAL","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"KAL","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"KAL","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProdu